      <title>日本取消公用事业补贴推高通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/japan-s-scrapping-of-utility-subsidies-to-push-inflation-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本逐步取消公用事业补贴的计划可能会在夏季将通胀推向3%，从而可能使日本央行对加息路径的思考变得复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/japan-s-scrapping-of-utility-subsidies-to-push-inflation-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:28:40 GMT</pubDate>
